ries)|Tempted]]''\n| [[Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation|MBC]]\n| Eun Tae-hee\n| Lead role\n| <ref name=\"gt\" />\n|}\n\n===Television show===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Network\n! Role\n! Notes\n! Ref.\n|-\n| 2015\u20132016\n| ''[[We Got Married (Season 4)|We Got Married]]''\n| [[Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation|MBC]]\n| Cast member\n| Paired up with [[Yook Sung-jae]]\n| <ref name=wgm /><ref>Park Jae Min. [http://osen.mt.co.kr/article/G1110168569 21\uc0b4 \uc721\uc131\uc7ac\u00b720\uc0b4 \uc870\uc774, \uaf2c\ub9c8\uc2e0\ub791\uc2e0\ubd80 \uac00\uc0c1\uacb0\ud63c \uc5b4\ub5a8\uae4c] ''OSEN'', June 13, 2015. Retrieved February 8, 2017.</ref>\n|-\n| 2016\u20132017\n| ''[[Trick & True]]''\n| [[Korean Broadcasting System|KBS]]\n| Fixed panelist\n| Since Episode 5\n| <ref>Yu Chan-hee. [http://tenasia.hankyung.com/archives/1065797 \u2018\ud2b8\ub9ad \uc564 \ud2b8\ub8e8\u2019 \ub808\ub4dc\ubca8\ubcb3 \uc870\uc774, \uc0ac\ub791 \uace0\ubc31\uc5d0 \u201c\ub098 \uc26c\uc6b4 \uc5ec\uc790 \uc544\ub2c8\uc57c\u201d] ''Ten Asia'', November 23, 2016. Retrieved January 26, 2017.</ref>\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2017\n|''[[Oppa Thinking]]''\n|MBC\n|Cast member\n|Pilot Episode\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://tenasia.hankyung.com/archives/1116513|title={{!}} '\uc624\ube60\uc0dd\uac01' \uacbd\ub9ac\u00b7\uc870\uc774\u00b7\ucc28\uc740\uc6b0, \ub3d9\uc694\uc5d0 \ub9de\ucdb0 '\uae5c\ucc0d \uc548\ubb34'\ud150\uc544\uc2dc\uc544|last=\uc7ac\ubc30\ud3ec\uae08\uc9c0>|first=<\u24d2 \u201c\ud150\uc544\uc2dc\uc544\u201d \ubb34\ub2e8\uc804\uc7ac|date=2017-01-19|website=\ud150\uc544\uc2dc\uc544|language=ko-KR|access-date=2018-12-17}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[King of Mask Singer]]''\n| MBC\n| Contestant\n| As \"Bandabi\" (Episodes 121\u2013122)\n| <ref name=\":1\">{{Cite news|author=Jang Jin-ri|title='\ubcf5\uba74\uac00\uc655' \ud30c\uc6cc\ub514\ubc14 \uc601\ud76c, \u65b0 \uac00\uc655 \ub4f1\uadf9\u2026\uc544\uae30\ud574\ub9c8\ub294 \ucf00\uc774\uc70c [\uc885\ud569]|url=http://osen.mt.co.kr/article/G